    {
      "beat_id": "B03",
      "act": "THE QUESTION",
      "estimated_duration_s": 9,
      "narration_text": "How can a pulse reverse phase dispersion without reversing the magnetic field or making fast spins slow? And what kinds of decay remain after refocusing?",
