      "act": "THE EXAMPLE",
      "estimated_duration_s": 13,
      "narration_text": "Suppose echo amplitudes measured at echo times fifty, one hundred, and two hundred milliseconds are zero point eight five, zero point seven two, and zero point five two. A simple e to minus t echo over T two fit gives about three hundred five milliseconds.",
