      "beat_id": "B11",
      "act": "PHASE BOOKKEEPING",
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "narration_text": "For a fixed offset, the first wait contributes plus delta omega tau. The pulse reverses its sign in the phase ordering; the second wait adds the same magnitude back toward zero. Net offset phase at two tau: zero.",
